266
00:16:05.050 --> 00:16:08.610
Now that we had these pieces together, we had the shRNA

267
00:16:08.670 --> 00:16:12.130
data, the omics data, and the computational infrastructure,

268
00:16:12.630 --> 00:16:16.050
now we could had enough to build the first map.

269
00:16:16.550 --> 00:16:20.370
So this is a publication where the terminology cancer dependency

