00:16:20.450 --> 00:16:21.750
map first appeared.

271
00:16:23.030 --> 00:16:24.930
And in this manuscript,

272
00:16:25.730 --> 00:16:26.210
we

273
00:16:27.670 --> 00:16:31.350
created the framework to link molecular features of the

274
00:16:31.430 --> 00:16:33.170
tumors to cancer dependencies.

275
00:16:34.190 --> 00:16:37.890
This proved possible. We identify many of the

276
00:16:37.910 --> 00:16:41.810
known oncogene addictions that took years to identify

277
00:16:41.889 --> 00:16:42.610
before this.

278
00:16:43.430 --> 00:16:44.040
For instance,

279
00:16:45.090 --> 00:16:48.930
dependency in KRAS mutant cell lines, BRAF dependency in BRAF mutant cell lines.

