00:21:03.306 --> 00:21:06.186
So I'm going to use that to illustrate how important this is.

352
00:21:06.886 --> 00:21:10.646
So I said that shRNA data is better and

353
00:21:10.706 --> 00:21:14.526
cleaner than CRISPR data, I'm sorry, is better and cleaner than shRNA,

