00:34:47.254 --> 00:34:50.894
are independent of publication. But early

578
00:34:51.074 --> 00:34:54.714
on, we decided that we were not going to link data releases to

579
00:34:54.734 --> 00:34:58.514
publication. This is because publications take a very long

