00:35:01.874 --> 00:35:04.094
data as we were generating the data.

582
00:35:04.194 --> 00:35:08.154
So every release, we've been releasing the data that we

583
00:35:08.194 --> 00:35:11.934
had available at that time so that the community will have the data

584
00:35:12.014 --> 00:35:15.694
available rather than waiting a few years for the manuscript.

585
00:35:17.774 --> 00:35:21.084
And also, there's a lot of impact that can be measured

586
00:35:21.814 --> 00:35:25.774
that also makes us very proud. All the academic labs that

587
00:35:25.874 --> 00:35:29.664
use the data on a regular basis in their lab to check on

588
00:35:29.694 --> 00:35:33.214
something they are working on. At a conference, we often see

