00:36:29.914 --> 00:36:33.454
So a number of years ago, Jesse Bohm and Muni Singh

605
00:36:33.614 --> 00:36:37.334
started the Cancer Cell Line Factory with the goal of

606
00:36:37.614 --> 00:36:40.934
generating models, and in particular for models that we didn't

607
00:36:40.974 --> 00:36:43.554
have any, or they were significantly

608
00:36:43.614 --> 00:36:47.282
underrepresented.So they did this, and they generated

