00:38:33.402 --> 00:38:36.502
we have focused mostly on single gene knockout and

638
00:38:36.582 --> 00:38:40.342
single drug sensitivity. But we know to

639
00:38:40.422 --> 00:38:44.122
amass some of the dependencies, we will need to use more than one gene to

640
00:38:44.142 --> 00:38:47.302
suppress more than one gene or maybe use drug and genes or drug/drug.

641
00:38:48.402 --> 00:38:52.202
So we started by focusing on paralogs.

642
00:38:52.962 --> 00:38:56.862
Paralogs are a class that they have a

643
00:38:56.902 --> 00:38:59.322
lot of redundancy, right? Because they are paralogs, and they are

