657
00:39:47.842 --> 00:39:51.542
you knock out both AKT1 and AKT2. This is what I'm

658
00:39:51.562 --> 00:39:53.162
highlighting here in this box.

659
00:39:54.342 --> 00:39:57.722
So for seeing this dependency, you have to knock out both.

660
00:39:58.002 --> 00:40:01.922
So this obviously has implications for anyone working on

661
00:40:01.962 --> 00:40:05.682
targeting paralog genes, whether it is better to have a more

662
00:40:05.762 --> 00:40:09.242
specific, less specific, and maybe biomarkers

663
00:40:09.862 --> 00:40:10.342
for that.

664
00:40:13.902 --> 00:40:17.162
So finally, the last gap I'm going to talk about here is the

